<h2 id="typography">Typography</h2>
<p>The Easy Read type scale is scoped to <code>nsw-easy-read-content</code>. It does not change standard page typography. Values use <code>rem</code> so browser zoom and text resizing continue to work; the pixel values below are equivalents based on the design system's 16px reference size, not a fixed root font size.</p>
